<subSubSection id="B6896573FFD1FF8FFFDFFF6DFDF57C6E" pageId="25" pageNumber="62" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="FE2C36F8FFD1FF8FFFDFFF6DFF357DE7" blockId="25.[107,222,176,194]" box="[107,222,176,194]" pageId="25" pageNumber="62">
<emphasis id="CCE7EAEAFFD1FF8FFFDFFF6DFF357DE7" bold="true" box="[107,222,176,194]" pageId="25" pageNumber="62">Comments</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FE2C36F8FFD1FF8FFFDEFF0BFEF27C0E" blockId="25.[106,1096,213,299]" pageId="25" pageNumber="62">
<taxonomicName id="39934D7BFFD1FF8FFFDEFF0BFEA47DC8" authorityName="Lonsdale &amp; Marshall" authorityYear="2007" box="[106,335,213,237]" class="Insecta" family="Clusiidae" genus="Heteromeringia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="apholis">
<emphasis id="CCE7EAEAFFD1FF8FFFDEFF0BFEA47DC8" box="[106,335,213,237]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="62">Heteromeringia apholis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a small, dark species, and the only New World 
<taxonomicName id="39934D7BFFD1FF8FFCE9FF0BFC1D7DC8" authorityName="CZERNY" authorityYear="1903" box="[861,1014,214,237]" class="Insecta" family="Clusiidae" genus="Heteromeringia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="CCE7EAEAFFD1FF8FFCE9FF0BFC1D7DC8" box="[861,1014,214,237]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="62">Heteromeringia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
outside of the 
<taxonomicName id="39934D7BFFD1FF8FFF19FF28FEFF7C29" authorityName="KERTESZ ER" authorityYear="1903" box="[173,276,245,268]" class="Insecta" family="Clusiidae" genus="Heteromeringia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="62" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="czernyi">
<emphasis id="CCE7EAEAFFD1FF8FFF19FF28FEFF7C29" box="[173,276,245,268]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="62">H. czernyi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group (possibly aside from two species as yet unknown from males) without an anepisternal disc.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FE2C36F8FFD1FF8FFFDFFEE4FDF57C6E" blockId="25.[107,542,313,337]" box="[107,542,313,337]" pageId="25" pageNumber="62">
